---
title: Thai-Spiced Pork Chops with Lemongrass-Infused Rice and Pineapple Salad
description: A little spicy, a little savoury and just the right amount of sweetness – these pork chops have those Thai cuisine vibes we've been dreaming about! The sweet and savoury train continues with a pineapple salad and fresh lemongrass and lime-infused rice.
